abstract: Actors and celebrities celebrate Oscars awards during Vanity Fair afterparty hosted at custom-designed space in Beverly Hills, Calif.
lead_paragraph: America’s royal couple strode in late, and the crowd couldn’t help itself. An onslaught of photos began.

headline.main: At Vanity Fair’s Oscars Party, Jay Z and Beyoncé Steal the Show
headline.print_headline: Dancing Is Contagious at Vanity Fair’s Party
